Package photos32.model

Class Photo

java.lang.Object
photos32.model.Photo
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Photo extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a photo with metadata such as filepath, caption, date/time of creation, and associated tags. Provides functionality to add and retrieve tags, check if a photo has a specific tag, and manage photo details.
